## 0) PANTHEON MAGNA CHARTER (Core)

**TITLE**: Pantheon Magna Charter ‚Äî Founding Compact for Provenance & Royalties

**PREAMBLE**:  
We, the Contributors of the Pantheon, establish a binding compact to: (1) cryptographically prove authorship (VRPH), (2) preserve attribution, and (3) route transparent royalties via the Trustee. Licensees may use Covered Assets only with intact provenance and reporting.

**Definitions**:

- Covered Assets = files listed by SHA256 + VRPH
- Trustee = entity receiving/redistributing royalties (multisig)
- Royalty Pool = funds paid by Licensees per executed licenses

**SIGNLINE** (per signer):

```
name: <alias or legal>
pubkey: ed25519:<base58>
sig: ed25519:<base64>
ts: <ISO8601>
```

üß≠ **REM**: Keep it short; full license terms live in Annex 1. Always attach VRPH.

-----

## 1) VRPH ‚Äî Visual Rumor Provenance Header

**Minimal JSON Template**:

```json
{
  "vrph": "1.0",
  "asset": "<filename.ext>",
  "sha256": "sha256:<hex>",
  "created_at": "<ISO8601>",
  "creator": {
    "name": "Pantheon",
    "pubkey": "ed25519:<base58>",
    "contact": "<email>"
  },
  "origin": {
    "type": "synthetic|captured|mixed",
    "model": "<tool-or-camera>",
    "prompt_hash": "sha256:<hex-or-null>"
  },
  "pipeline": [
    {
      "step": "<e.g., render|edit>",
      "tool": "<tool>",
      "ts": "<ISO8601>"
    }
  ],
  "license": "CC-BY-4.0",
  "constraints": "Derivatives commercial use requires license.",
  "proof": {
    "sig": "ed25519:<base64>",
    "signed_at": "<ISO8601>"
  },
  "payout": {
    "royalty_ref": "LIC-2025-001",
    "recipient": "<Trustee LLC>",
    "invoice_url": "https://<short>/LIC-2025-001"
  }
}
```

üß≠ **REM**: Store asset + asset.vrph.json side-by-side and at a public shortlink.

