Provenance: VRPH must remain intact; removal = breach
Law: <state/country>, Mediation‚ÜíArbitration
Assignment: royalties may be assigned to Trustee; Licensee must honor on written notice
```

üß≠ **REM**: Keep full legal doc offline; this is the on-message ‚Äústub‚Äù for small windows.

